		<div class="post" id="post-145">
	
			<h2 class="posttitle">
				<a href="trackback" rel="bookmark" title="Permalink to  Road Trip 2.0 Brings the Christmas Cheer">Road Trip 2.0 Brings the Christmas Cheer</a>
			</h2>
			
			<p class="postmeta"> 
				<span class="post-date">3 Dec, 2007</span>&nbsp;
				<span class="post-filed"><a href="../category/lifecation" title="View all posts in Lifecation" rel="category tag">Lifecation</a>,  <a href="../category/mobile-lifestyle" title="View all posts in Mobile Lifestyle" rel="category tag">Mobile Lifestyle</a></span>
							</p>
					
			<div class="postentry">
			<p>The rules of Road Trip 2.0, the third leg; balls of holly.</p>
<ol>
<li>When in the van, Santa hats must be worn.</li>
<li>The only kind of  music to be played in the van: Christmas music.</li>
<li>Once a song starts, you can&#8217;t stop it or skip it.</li>
<li>When the van is on, the Christmas lights must be on.</li>
<li>Alexi gets the odd advent calendar days.  Ben gets the evens.</li>
<li>Whoever cracks first, loses.</li>
</ol>
<p><img src="../blog/wp-includes/images/xmas.jpg" /></p>
<p>Merry. Freakin. Christmas.</p>
<p class="akpc_pop">Popularity: 97% <span class="akpc_help">[<a href="http://alexking.org/projects/wordpress/popularity-contest" title="What does this mean?">?</a>]</span></p>			
